1
00:00:18,150 --> 00:00:19,150
Who are you?

2
00:00:20,150 --> 00:00:21,150
Tian. It's blood.

3
00:00:21,350 --> 00:00:23,150
What's wrong?

4
00:00:23,450 --> 00:00:24,150
Someone attacked me.

5
00:00:24,650 --> 00:00:25,150
I almost killed you, Tian.

6
00:00:26,150 --> 00:00:27,150
Tian, dodge!

7
00:00:28,150 --> 00:00:30,150
Hurry, go! Go, Tian. Quickly!

8
00:00:30,650 --> 00:00:33,150
So this means you are really close to Tian?

9
00:00:33,650 --> 00:00:34,150
He is like a benefactor for my siblings.

10
00:00:35,150 --> 00:00:37,150
So I have choices for you.

11
00:00:38,150 --> 00:00:40,150
I thought we'd never meet again, Doctor Qi.

12
00:00:40,450 --> 00:00:41,150
Doctor Qi.

13
00:00:41,650 --> 00:00:43,150
Do you know this mushroom?

14
00:00:44,150 --> 00:00:46,150
This mushroom is called blood sucking mushroom.

15
00:00:46,450 --> 00:00:49,150
this mushroom grew from the remains of living things.

16
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:51,150
Dong, a worker at my house has died.

17
00:00:51,450 --> 00:00:52,150
His body disappeared.

18
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:55,150
The whole family suspected that it was Li who did it.

19
00:00:55,450 --> 00:00:57,150
So what do you think?

20
00:00:57,650 --> 00:00:59,150
I suspect that it was Li too.

21
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:01,150
Try digging the area where this mushroom grew

22
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:03,150
and see if there is anything there.

23
00:01:03,650 --> 00:01:06,150
Tell me immediately if you find something. I will meet you in Phra Nakhon.

24
00:01:06,650 --> 00:01:08,150
A human tooth.

25
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:57,150
Yang, since the mushrooms are all dead,

26
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:59,150
what are you looking for.

27
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:02,150
I still have a doubt.

28
00:03:02,450 --> 00:03:03,150
The mushrooms suddenly died.

29
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:07,150
I want to check again in case we miss something.

30
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,150
Yes.

31
00:03:11,150 --> 00:03:12,150
Yang.

32
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:15,150
Someone dug the ground here.

33
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:21,150
Who did this?

34
00:03:30,150 --> 00:03:31,150
Yang.

35
00:03:31,450 --> 00:03:35,150
What if Madam and Jia dug the soil here?

36
00:03:35,850 --> 00:03:37,150
I don't know who did this

37
00:03:37,650 --> 00:03:40,150
but if it was really the two of them, It's dangerous.

38
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:42,150
We must be careful.

39
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:48,150
Please, hope it was just Aunt Kham digging for the mushrooms.

40
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:53,150
Bua, Yang.

41
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,150
Mr. Song would like to see you two.

42
00:04:27,150 --> 00:04:29,150
You two.

43
00:04:31,150 --> 00:04:33,150
Why did you go to the mound at the back of the house?

44
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:38,150
Did you know something about those mushrooms?

45
00:04:39,150 --> 00:04:41,150
Do you know about the mushrooms?

46
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:43,150
So it's actually you guys

47
00:04:44,150 --> 00:04:45,150
who gave Doctor Qi the mushrooms.

48
00:04:48,150 --> 00:04:49,150
That's why…

49
00:04:50,150 --> 00:04:52,150
you asked for Doctor Qi.

50
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:56,150
Why do you suspect the mushrooms?

51
00:04:58,150 --> 00:05:01,150
Mr. Yang, please tell him.

52
00:05:01,650 --> 00:05:03,150
So there will be someone to help us find the truth.

53
00:05:13,150 --> 00:05:14,150
There's nothing.

54
00:05:16,150 --> 00:05:17,150
I just think that the mushroom is weird.

55
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:21,150
So I asked about this, but it isn't that important.

56
00:05:23,150 --> 00:05:25,150
Mr. Yang, why are you saying this?

57
00:05:27,150 --> 00:05:28,150
Yang.

58
00:05:29,150 --> 00:05:30,150
Last time, you also lied to me

59
00:05:31,150 --> 00:05:33,150
regarding Tian's Secret.

60
00:05:34,150 --> 00:05:35,150
You said you secretly went out

61
00:05:36,150 --> 00:05:37,150
but you told me another thing.

62
00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:41,150
Do you think I will believe you this time?

63
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:46,150
Why would you suddenly take the mushrooms to ask Doctor Qi

64
00:05:47,150 --> 00:05:48,150
if you don't doubt it?

65
00:05:48,650 --> 00:05:51,150
You said I was lying and lying again.

66
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:55,150
Am I wrong if I just wanted to know some nonsense?

67
00:05:56,150 --> 00:05:59,150
I already told you that it doesn't matter at all.

68
00:06:01,150 --> 00:06:02,150
Yang.

69
00:06:04,150 --> 00:06:06,150
The more you are like this,

70
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:10,150
the more I'm confident that this is a big deal.

71
00:06:13,150 --> 00:06:16,150
What's the secret that you can't tell me?

72
00:06:19,150 --> 00:06:22,150
Or does that mushroom have something to do with Li?

73
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:27,150
Probably not.

74
00:06:30,150 --> 00:06:33,150
Because if it's just about Li, you probably wouldn't hide it this much.

75
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:42,150
Or is it related to…

76
00:06:45,150 --> 00:06:47,150
Is it related to Tian's secret?

77
00:06:52,150 --> 00:06:53,150
Yang.

78
00:06:56,150 --> 00:06:57,150
Tell me.

79
00:07:02,150 --> 00:07:03,150
Even if you kill me,

80
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:05,150
I have nothing to say.

81
00:07:07,150 --> 00:07:09,150
Is this really that serious?

82
00:07:13,150 --> 00:07:15,150
Or does it affect the Song Family?

83
00:07:18,150 --> 00:07:20,150
I think we're done talking. Excuse me.

84
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:21,150
Yang!

85
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:23,150
Where are you going?

86
00:07:23,450 --> 00:07:24,150
Madam.

87
00:07:38,150 --> 00:07:39,150
I brought herbal soup for Mr. Song.

88
00:07:42,150 --> 00:07:44,150
So what are you talking now?

89
00:07:45,150 --> 00:07:47,150
I've never seen you requesting for Bua and Yang here.

90
00:07:52,150 --> 00:07:54,150
Or is there something that I shouldn't know?

91
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:07,150
It's about Yang.

92
00:08:08,150 --> 00:08:09,150
He went out to have fun again.

93
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:12,150
So I have to give him a lesson.

94
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:19,150
Sir, please don't scold Mr. Yang.

95
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:23,150
Bua, let him do it.

96
00:08:24,150 --> 00:08:26,150
He'll suffocate if he doesn't curse me.

97
00:08:27,150 --> 00:08:31,150
Yang, you're getting on my nerves. Go!

98
00:08:31,450 --> 00:08:32,150
Go away!

99
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:36,150
Please excuse me.

100
00:08:37,150 --> 00:08:40,150
Yang, are you alright?

101
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:41,150
Mr. Yang!

102
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:48,150
Sir.

103
00:08:49,150 --> 00:08:51,150
Yang is not a successor like Tian.

104
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:54,150
Don't force him.

105
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:10,150
Why didn't you tell Mr. Song the truth

106
00:09:10,650 --> 00:09:12,150
of what we think or doubt?

107
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:16,150
Isn't it better to have Mr. Song help us find the truth?

108
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:19,150
I had to tell Father like that

109
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:22,150
because if Madam and Li the really did it,

110
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:25,150
the two of them did it to protect Tian.

111
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:28,150
What if the two of them were exposed?

112
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:30,150
The person who will be in trouble the most is Tian.

113
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:34,150
And his secret will be revealed to others.

114
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:36,150
Why?

115
00:09:36,650 --> 00:09:39,150
Is Tian's secret really that serious?

116
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:42,150
Even Mr. Song can't know it at all?

117
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:49,150
For me, his secret is not serious or harmful to anyone.

118
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:53,150
But others, especially my father, should never know this.

119
00:09:56,150 --> 00:09:59,150
You don't have to know his secret.

120
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:03,150
So you won't be discouraged because you can't find a way out for Tian like me.

121
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,150
Yang.

122
00:10:05,650 --> 00:10:08,150
But right now, Mr. Song suspects us a lot.

123
00:10:08,650 --> 00:10:12,150
He even secretly called the two of us to talk behind Madam Li.

124
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:14,150
He probably doubted Madam as well.

125
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:18,150
That's right. I'm afraid that if Father finds out the truth,

126
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,150
it's going to be a big deal.

127
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:26,150
And will we let the guilty person go unpunished?

128
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:30,150
If we remain silent, we help the villain cover up

129
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:33,150
when the wicked should be punished.

130
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:36,150
But if we do what is right,

131
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:39,150
an innocent person like Tian will suffer.

132
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:43,150
Oh, Yang.

133
00:10:47,150 --> 00:10:49,150
I don't know how to help Tian.

134
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:11,150
What's up? Do you know Tian's secret?

135
00:11:11,650 --> 00:11:13,150
Oh, not yet, Madam.

136
00:11:13,650 --> 00:11:16,150
I think Mr. Yang hang out with Bua everyday to the point that he forgets

137
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:18,150
which one is his real mother.

138
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:23,150
I don't understand my son at all. As a mother, I can't force him.

139
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:24,150
Forget it, Madam.

140
00:11:24,650 --> 00:11:28,150
He hasn't told even Bua that he loves like a real mother.

141
00:11:28,850 --> 00:11:29,150
Bitch.

142
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:48,150
Can't you sleep?

143
00:11:57,150 --> 00:11:58,150
I couldn't either.

144
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:03,150
I'm worried about Tian.

145
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:07,150
So you really don't know

146
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:09,150
what secrets does Tian have?

147
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:12,150
I really don't know, Sir.

148
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:17,150
I couldn’t figure out

149
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:21,150
what secret does he hide from me?

150
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,150
Oh.

151
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:30,150
Or is it about Pin?

152
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:33,150
Because every time I talk about marriage,

153
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:36,150
he looked unhappy.

154
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:39,150
It might be possible.

155
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:43,150
Because I've seen Tian look worried about not wanting to marry Lady Pin.

156
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:51,150
Then Mr. Tian's secret is probably related to marriage, Sir.

157
00:12:55,150 --> 00:12:56,150
Oh.

158
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:58,150
Or is it true that Mr. Tian has...
Oh.

159
00:12:58,150 --> 00:12:59,150
Or is it true that Mr. Tian has...

160
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:00,150
What is it?

161
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:03,150
He secretly has a wife and child hidden outside the house.

162
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:08,150
Because lately he likes to go out often, right?

163
00:13:08,450 --> 00:13:13,150
If he has a wife and kid, why does he have to hide that?

164
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:18,150
Maybe it's because that woman is inferior

165
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:20,150
or maybe she's a bad woman,

166
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:23,150
not suitable for Mr. Tian, so it must conceal them.

167
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:27,150
If it's just that,

168
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:30,150
I couldn't see why Yang and Tian have to cover up so much.

169
00:13:32,150 --> 00:13:33,150
Or...

170
00:13:34,150 --> 00:13:35,150
Tian had an affair with a married wife?

171
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:38,150
The woman already has a family.

172
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:41,150
This is possible, Sir.

173
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:45,150
If he steals someone's wife, he will have to hide it.

174
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:51,150
Such a disgrace would cause the Song Family to be attacked.

175
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:53,150
Bua.

176
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:57,150
Keep an eye on Tian and Yang well.

177
00:13:57,650 --> 00:13:59,150
If something slips out, report me immediately.

178
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,150
Yes, Sir.

179
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:04,150
Bao, you follow Tian.

180
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:09,150
If he goes outside, see what he does and who he meets.

181
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:11,150
Yes, Sir.

182
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:18,150
This one.

183
00:14:19,150 --> 00:14:20,150
Ratchaburi.

184
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:24,150
This one is Ayutthaya.

185
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:28,150
I hired someone to take pictures so we can give these to billionaires,

186
00:14:29,150 --> 00:14:31,150
or the merchants I know in case they might be interested.

187
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:35,150
And here, this one.

188
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:38,150
I think this one can be sold at a high price.

189
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:45,150
I myself have little knowledge of these things.

190
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:48,150
If I sell them, the price will be lowballed for sure.

191
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:53,150
Thanks for taking care of this matter for me.

192
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:10,150
Yang.

193
00:15:12,150 --> 00:15:13,150
Is my stuff causing you any inconvenience or discomfort?

194
00:15:18,150 --> 00:15:21,150
No, why do you think that?

195
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:24,150
You look different.

196
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:27,150
It's not like every time we meet.

197
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:33,150
Actually…

198
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:38,150
I have something that stuck in my mind.

199
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:40,150
But I don't know how to handle it.

200
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:44,150
Can I ask you something?

201
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:48,150
If one day I find out about something

202
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:50,150
which is very serious,

203
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:52,150
and if I say it out,

204
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:54,150
the one I love will suffer.

205
00:15:55,150 --> 00:15:59,150
But if I don't say and do nothing,

206
00:15:59,450 --> 00:16:00,150
and let this quiet,

207
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:03,150
this will affect him in the future anyway.

208
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:06,150
What should I do?

209
00:16:07,150 --> 00:16:11,150
So what is it that you really want?

210
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:16,150
Whatever that my loved one will not be in trouble.

211
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:25,150
You said it yourself that it will affect him in the future.

212
00:16:26,150 --> 00:16:27,150
So why not let him choose by himself?

213
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:30,150
Whether he is ready to face it now

214
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:35,150
or he wants to buy more time to wait for the consequence in the future.

215
00:16:36,150 --> 00:16:40,150
Sometimes you have to let him decide on his own matter himself.

216
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:44,150
He may be able to make better decisions than anyone else.

217
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:59,150
Herbal soup.

218
00:17:05,150 --> 00:17:06,150
Thanks.

219
00:17:22,150 --> 00:17:23,150
What's wrong?

220
00:17:23,850 --> 00:17:26,150
I'm going to check the work at the warehouse.

221
00:17:26,650 --> 00:17:28,150
You can let Tian oversee it.

222
00:17:29,150 --> 00:17:30,150
You are still not feeling well.

223
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:34,150
It's okay, I'd better go out and see it myself.

224
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:37,150
Bao.

225
00:17:38,150 --> 00:17:39,150
Bring me the walking stick.

226
00:18:25,150 --> 00:18:26,150
A tooth?

227
00:18:29,150 --> 00:18:31,150
This is a human tooth.

228
00:18:32,150 --> 00:18:33,150
Yes, Doctor Qi.

229
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:37,150
I dug the soil where the mushroom grew.

230
00:18:39,150 --> 00:18:42,150
I only found one tooth no matter how hard I dug it.

231
00:18:43,150 --> 00:18:45,150
Maybe it was related to Dong's body that had disappeared earlier.

232
00:18:46,150 --> 00:18:49,150
But I only found a tooth.

233
00:18:49,450 --> 00:18:52,150
Where did the other pieces go, Doctor?

234
00:18:54,150 --> 00:18:55,150
Something…

235
00:18:57,150 --> 00:19:01,150
can destroy the remains of living beings without a trace.

236
00:19:05,150 --> 00:19:06,150
Sir.

237
00:19:07,150 --> 00:19:09,150
Besides Madam Li and Jia,

238
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:14,150
do you think there is anyone else suspicious?

239
00:19:16,150 --> 00:19:19,150
For me, everyone seems suspicious right now.

240
00:19:21,150 --> 00:19:23,150
Everything seems to be related to Tian's secret.

241
00:19:25,150 --> 00:19:28,150
But I don't know what his secret is.

242
00:19:57,150 --> 00:19:58,150
Yang.

243
00:19:59,150 --> 00:20:00,150
Did you meet Lady Pin today? You've been gone all day.

244
00:20:09,150 --> 00:20:10,150
What's wrong?

245
00:20:11,150 --> 00:20:12,150
Tian.

246
00:20:13,150 --> 00:20:16,150
You know, right? No matter what happens,

247
00:20:18,150 --> 00:20:19,150
I will always be by your side.

248
00:21:01,150 --> 00:21:02,150
This is a mushroom that grows behind our house.

249
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:05,150
Tian.

250
00:21:06,150 --> 00:21:08,150
Listen to me carefully.

251
00:21:09,150 --> 00:21:12,150
This matter is very important and it is directly related to you.

252
00:21:15,150 --> 00:21:20,150
At first, I thought I'd be secretly investigating this without affecting you.

253
00:21:21,150 --> 00:21:25,150
But the more I searched for the truth, the more it makes you difficult.

254
00:21:28,150 --> 00:21:29,150
This mushroom...

255
00:21:31,150 --> 00:21:33,150
It's called a blood sucking mushroom.

256
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:40,150
It was produced by mixing a kind of orchid with special ingredients.

257
00:21:41,150 --> 00:21:44,150
And it can grow in the remains of living things.

258
00:21:45,150 --> 00:21:47,150
Remains of living things?

259
00:21:48,150 --> 00:21:49,150
Tian.

260
00:21:50,150 --> 00:21:51,150
I think that…

261
00:21:53,150 --> 00:21:55,150
It probably grew from Dong's corpse.

262
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:56,150
Dong's corpse?

263
00:22:04,150 --> 00:22:05,150
So that day...

264
00:22:08,150 --> 00:22:09,150
Do you remember?

265
00:22:11,150 --> 00:22:14,150
When we went to open the coffin, the body was an old man's.

266
00:22:15,150 --> 00:22:16,150
And before that,

267
00:22:17,150 --> 00:22:19,150
Madam Li let Auntie Jia sleep there and watch Dong's body.

268
00:22:22,150 --> 00:22:24,150
And I think she used that chance

269
00:22:25,150 --> 00:22:27,150
to switch Dong's body and buried it at the back of our house.

270
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:29,150
It might not be what you think.

271
00:22:29,250 --> 00:22:30,150
Tian.

272
00:22:31,150 --> 00:22:32,150
So didn't you wonder

273
00:22:33,150 --> 00:22:36,150
why everyone in the house ate the mushrooms, but no one fell ill?

274
00:22:37,150 --> 00:22:39,150
Only Madam Li

275
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:43,150
who ate a mushroom vomited and had a fever.

276
00:22:44,150 --> 00:22:47,150
Because she knew where that mushroom came from.

277
00:22:48,150 --> 00:22:52,150
Aunt Jia is also good at preparing herbs and medicine.

278
00:22:54,150 --> 00:22:56,150
And who else would have thought of doing something like this?

279
00:23:16,150 --> 00:23:17,150
Tian.

280
00:23:18,150 --> 00:23:20,150
I'm sorry to have to say this.

281
00:23:23,150 --> 00:23:26,150
But I think this will affect you in the future.

282
00:23:27,150 --> 00:23:30,150
I want you to prepare and find a way to deal with it beforehand.

283
00:23:31,150 --> 00:23:32,150
If it is true,

284
00:23:34,150 --> 00:23:35,150
how am I going to handle it?

285
00:23:37,150 --> 00:23:40,150
Mother is the villain who killed a man.

286
00:23:41,150 --> 00:23:42,150
And I can't tell anyone.

287
00:23:48,150 --> 00:23:49,150
Yang.

288
00:23:54,150 --> 00:23:56,150
I really don't know what to do.

289
00:23:57,150 --> 00:23:58,150
Tian.

290
00:23:59,150 --> 00:24:02,150
All of this happened because of me.

291
00:24:03,150 --> 00:24:04,150
Because of me.

292
00:24:06,150 --> 00:24:07,150
Mother did this…

293
00:24:09,150 --> 00:24:12,150
because she wanted to hide my secret.

294
00:24:15,150 --> 00:24:16,150
Yang.

295
00:24:17,150 --> 00:24:20,150
Do you know how miserable I am?

296
00:24:22,150 --> 00:24:24,150
I have to live in misery.

297
00:24:26,150 --> 00:24:29,150
Suffering because of this damn secret.

298
00:24:34,150 --> 00:24:36,150
Because of the secret.

299
00:24:38,150 --> 00:24:39,150
The secret…

300
00:24:51,150 --> 00:24:52,150
The secret…

301
00:24:57,150 --> 00:24:58,150
The secret that I am...

302
00:24:59,150 --> 00:25:00,150
Don't say it.

303
00:25:12,150 --> 00:25:13,150
You don't have to say anything now.

304
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:18,150
Yang.

305
00:25:19,150 --> 00:25:20,150
Don't say it.

306
00:25:24,150 --> 00:25:26,150
Stay still, don't speak.

307
00:25:33,150 --> 00:25:36,150
Yang, this bastard.

308
00:25:40,150 --> 00:25:41,150
By the way, those mushrooms…

309
00:26:00,150 --> 00:26:04,150
Are you sure that the mushrooms we ate came from Dong's corpse?

310
00:26:05,150 --> 00:26:06,150
I shouldn't eat too much.

311
00:26:07,150 --> 00:26:08,150
That's what I heard.

312
00:26:09,150 --> 00:26:11,150
Should we tell Mr. Song about this?

313
00:26:12,150 --> 00:26:12,950
No.

314
00:26:13,150 --> 00:26:16,150
I think every time we fail, it's because we always rant and make it a big deal.

315
00:26:17,150 --> 00:26:20,150
If what I heard about the mushrooms is true,

316
00:26:20,550 --> 00:26:25,150
we will have to find evidence to catch the villain red-handed.

317
00:26:27,150 --> 00:26:31,150
If Jia was the one who actually made the mushroom grow from the corpse,

318
00:26:32,150 --> 00:26:35,150
we'll have to figure out how she did it.

319
00:26:36,150 --> 00:26:41,150
And we had to catch her for working with Madam Li to kill Dong

320
00:26:41,650 --> 00:26:43,150
to conceal a secret for Tian.

321
00:26:44,150 --> 00:26:48,150
They deserves the death penalty for killing someone cruelly like this.

322
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:49,150
Correct.

323
00:26:51,150 --> 00:26:52,150
And if two of them die,

324
00:26:53,150 --> 00:27:00,150
My son, Yang will inherit the position from Mr. Song without anyone interfering.

325
00:27:12,150 --> 00:27:13,150
Who's in my room?

326
00:27:19,150 --> 00:27:20,150
Who are you?

327
00:27:21,150 --> 00:27:22,150
Madam.

328
00:27:23,150 --> 00:27:24,150
Tian.

329
00:27:31,150 --> 00:27:32,150
What are you doing?

330
00:27:32,650 --> 00:27:34,150
You ask me what I am doing?

331
00:27:36,150 --> 00:27:39,150
I'm here to find out what you and Aunt Jia are hiding from me.

332
00:27:41,150 --> 00:27:43,150
What you use to kill a man, Mother.

333
00:27:47,150 --> 00:27:48,150
Mother.

334
00:27:49,150 --> 00:27:50,150
Aunt Jia, Aunt Jia.

335
00:27:50,550 --> 00:27:52,450
Aunt Jia, give it to me. Aunt Jia. Give it to me now.

336
00:27:52,450 --> 00:27:53,150
Tian, Tian, what are you doing?
Aunt Jia, give it to me. Aunt Jia. Give it to me now.

337
00:27:53,150 --> 00:27:54,150
Tian, Tian, what are you doing?

338
00:27:56,150 --> 00:27:57,150
Mother.

339
00:27:58,150 --> 00:28:03,150
I know it already that the mushrooms in our backyards grew from Dong's corpse.

340
00:28:06,150 --> 00:28:07,150
Nonsense.

341
00:28:09,150 --> 00:28:11,150
Where did you hear this?

342
00:28:12,150 --> 00:28:13,150
Don't listen to what other people say.

343
00:28:14,150 --> 00:28:15,150
They slandered me and Madam.

344
00:28:16,150 --> 00:28:17,150
Neither of us killed Dong.

345
00:28:17,250 --> 00:28:18,150
If you didn't kill him,

346
00:28:19,150 --> 00:28:21,150
why did you have to swap his body with someone else?

347
00:28:28,150 --> 00:28:29,150
Why?

348
00:28:32,150 --> 00:28:33,150
Before the funeral,

349
00:28:35,150 --> 00:28:38,150
you received an order from Mother to watch over Dong's body.

350
00:28:40,150 --> 00:28:42,150
Is there a reason or a necessity

351
00:28:43,150 --> 00:28:46,150
for a butler of Song Family's First Madam to take care of a body of an ordinary people like that?

352
00:28:50,150 --> 00:28:51,150
Why?

353
00:28:54,150 --> 00:28:56,150
If you think that I and Jia really did it,

354
00:28:57,150 --> 00:28:59,150
go inform the authorities and your father to arrest me.

355
00:29:02,150 --> 00:29:03,150
Mother.

356
00:29:04,150 --> 00:29:05,150
Just go!

357
00:29:34,150 --> 00:29:36,150
Tian! Tian!

358
00:29:39,150 --> 00:29:41,150
Where are you going?

359
00:29:41,450 --> 00:29:43,150
Tian, stop now.

360
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:45,150
Mr. Tian, what are you going to do?

361
00:29:46,150 --> 00:29:49,150
What are you doing? Stop!

362
00:29:50,150 --> 00:29:51,150
Tian, stop!

363
00:29:52,150 --> 00:29:53,150
What are you doing?

364
00:29:54,150 --> 00:29:55,150
I will tell everyone the truth.

365
00:29:56,150 --> 00:29:58,150
I don't want to keep it a secret anymore, Mother.

366
00:29:59,150 --> 00:30:00,150
You can't.

367
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:03,350
Do you know that if you tell everyone, you will lose everything?

368
00:30:03,350 --> 00:30:04,150
I know it.
Do you know that if you tell everyone, you will lose everything?

369
00:30:04,150 --> 00:30:04,550
I know it.

370
00:30:05,150 --> 00:30:06,150
I do.

371
00:30:09,150 --> 00:30:11,150
I'm willing to lose everything.

372
00:30:12,150 --> 00:30:13,150
But I don't want you or anyone

373
00:30:14,150 --> 00:30:17,150
to be in trouble because you have to hide my secret anymore.

374
00:30:24,150 --> 00:30:26,150
Tian! Tian!

375
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:27,150
What are you doing?

376
00:30:31,150 --> 00:30:32,150
Mr. Tian, Mr. Yang.

377
00:30:33,150 --> 00:30:34,150
Mr. Tian, Mr. Yang.

378
00:30:35,150 --> 00:30:36,150
What's the matter?

379
00:30:39,150 --> 00:30:41,150
Why are you summoning us at this time?

380
00:30:42,150 --> 00:30:43,150
Yeah, what's wrong?

381
00:30:49,150 --> 00:30:50,150
What's going on here?

382
00:30:53,150 --> 00:30:54,150
What happened?

383
00:30:55,150 --> 00:30:57,150
Hitting the gong at this time, or is there a thief?

384
00:30:59,150 --> 00:31:00,150
Or a fire?

385
00:31:01,150 --> 00:31:02,150
A thief?

386
00:31:02,350 --> 00:31:04,150
Did you check carefully? Have you looked at the garage yet?

387
00:31:04,350 --> 00:31:05,150
Did you forget to close the window?

388
00:31:06,150 --> 00:31:07,150
Tian.

389
00:31:09,150 --> 00:31:10,150
If you say it,

390
00:31:11,150 --> 00:31:13,150
get ready to attend my funeral.

391
00:31:23,150 --> 00:31:25,150
Hey everyone, can you be quiet?

392
00:31:28,150 --> 00:31:29,150
So what is it, Tian?

393
00:31:31,150 --> 00:31:32,150
What's going on?

394
00:31:35,150 --> 00:31:36,150
Tian.

395
00:31:56,150 --> 00:31:58,150
Or someone died?

396
00:32:04,150 --> 00:32:05,150
Well…

397
00:32:07,150 --> 00:32:09,150
Tian and I saw a snake.

398
00:32:10,150 --> 00:32:13,150
We were shocked, so we called everyone to help us catch it.

399
00:32:45,150 --> 00:32:46,150
Is it true?

400
00:32:52,150 --> 00:32:53,150
Yes, Father.

401
00:33:26,150 --> 00:33:28,150
What are you going to do about Tian?

402
00:33:29,150 --> 00:33:30,150
Let him go for now.

403
00:33:31,150 --> 00:33:32,150
Now he's sad.

404
00:33:33,150 --> 00:33:35,150
I will find a chance to talk to him later.

405
00:33:37,150 --> 00:33:39,150
Who gave Mr. Tian the mushrooms?

406
00:33:40,150 --> 00:33:43,150
Whoever the person is, we have to find out.

407
00:33:44,150 --> 00:33:46,150
What we have to do now,

408
00:33:46,450 --> 00:33:50,150
in addition to making Tian take the position as quickly as possible,

409
00:33:51,150 --> 00:33:55,150
we have to find out who knows about this mushroom.

410
00:34:02,150 --> 00:34:06,150
You suspect Mr. Tian hitting the gong last night?

411
00:34:07,150 --> 00:34:08,150
Yes.

412
00:34:09,150 --> 00:34:10,150
I don't believe

413
00:34:11,150 --> 00:34:14,150
that he called everyone to catch the snake as Li said.

414
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:17,150
It must be a secret about Tian.

415
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:22,150
Because both mother and son acted strange.

416
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:24,150
Yes, Sir.

417
00:34:24,850 --> 00:34:25,150
Sir.

418
00:34:27,150 --> 00:34:30,150
Bao, how was it?

419
00:34:30,350 --> 00:34:32,150
I have investigated.

420
00:34:33,150 --> 00:34:36,150
Mr. Tian likes to hang around Mr. Ma's neighborhood.

421
00:34:37,150 --> 00:34:39,150
And the locals are friendly with him.

422
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:42,150
The girls are interested in him quite a lot.

423
00:34:43,150 --> 00:34:47,150
But Mr. Tian is not particularly interested in any of them.

424
00:34:47,850 --> 00:34:49,150
Then Tian's secret

425
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:51,150
is probably not about women.

426
00:34:54,150 --> 00:34:55,150
What exactly is it?

427
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:26,150
Where are you going?

428
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:29,150
Where are you going, pretty?

429
00:35:30,150 --> 00:35:31,150
Want us to walk you home?

430
00:35:31,650 --> 00:35:33,150
It's okay, I'm almost there.

431
00:35:35,150 --> 00:35:37,150
You're sweet, your skin is also fair.

432
00:35:38,150 --> 00:35:39,150
Your breast is…

433
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:42,150
Crazy bastard.

434
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:46,150
Scold at me, scold again. It's very exciting. I like it.

435
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:55,150
Follow her quickly.

436
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:59,150
Excuse me, please help me, these bastards are going to kidnap me.

437
00:36:03,150 --> 00:36:04,150
Acting like a hooker.

438
00:36:05,150 --> 00:36:08,150
If you don't want a husband, then why are you dressed to seduce men?

439
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,150
It's my business, bastard.

440
00:36:12,150 --> 00:36:15,150
No matter how she dresses, it's up to her. What that's got to do with it?

441
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:19,150
It's her body, she can dress up anything.

442
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:23,150
You guys have no right to harass or hurt her.

443
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:26,150
So is it your business too? Don't get in my way.

444
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:19,150
Let's go.

445
00:37:20,150 --> 00:37:21,150
Hurry.

446
00:37:21,350 --> 00:37:22,150
Quickly.

447
00:37:26,150 --> 00:37:27,150
Thank you very much.

448
00:37:29,150 --> 00:37:31,150
Are you hurt?

449
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:33,150
Can I have a look?

450
00:37:36,150 --> 00:37:38,150
So what are you doing here?

451
00:37:54,150 --> 00:37:55,150
Sir.

452
00:37:57,150 --> 00:37:59,150
Someone wants to apply for a job.

453
00:38:18,150 --> 00:38:19,150
Jiu.

454
00:38:21,150 --> 00:38:22,150
Do you know each other?

455
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:44,150
I'm really worried about you.

456
00:38:44,150 --> 00:38:48,550
Since someone tried to shoot me that day, I don't know how you've been.

457
00:38:48,550 --> 00:38:50,150
Where have you been?

458
00:38:50,150 --> 00:38:54,150
I went to see you at home but your house closed all the time.

459
00:38:54,150 --> 00:38:56,150
I moved out.

460
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,150
Why did you move out?

461
00:39:00,150 --> 00:39:03,150
Because of the culprit? Who are they?

462
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:05,150
It doesn't matter.

463
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:08,150
Those who shot you were just thieves.

464
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:12,150
They might think that you seemed to have money, so I wanted to rob you.

465
00:39:14,150 --> 00:39:16,150
Actually, I moved out because

466
00:39:17,150 --> 00:39:20,150
I don't have money to pay rent.

467
00:39:21,150 --> 00:39:25,650
I think of what you said. If I was in trouble, I should come to you.

468
00:39:26,250 --> 00:39:28,150
What about Mei and Fu?

469
00:39:28,150 --> 00:39:30,150
Where are they now?

470
00:39:30,150 --> 00:39:33,150
Why don't you bring them along?

471
00:39:33,150 --> 00:39:36,150
I sent them to live with my relative right now.

472
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:43,150
You don't have to worry about your job and accommodation.

473
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:45,150
So...

474
00:39:46,150 --> 00:39:47,550
What do you want to do?

475
00:39:49,250 --> 00:39:51,150
Do you do an account?

476
00:39:53,150 --> 00:39:55,150
Or the paperwork?

477
00:39:56,150 --> 00:39:57,150
No.

478
00:39:58,150 --> 00:40:01,550
You don't want to do accounting or paperwork.

479
00:40:02,150 --> 00:40:04,150
So what would you like to work on?

480
00:40:04,550 --> 00:40:06,150
I'm illiterate.

481
00:40:08,050 --> 00:40:10,150
I can't read and write.

482
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:13,550
I can't do the job you said.

483
00:40:14,150 --> 00:40:16,150
I can only do the labor job.

484
00:40:16,850 --> 00:40:22,500
You can't write or read, but you learn.

485
00:40:25,150 --> 00:40:27,150
I'll be the one to teach you.

486
00:40:30,150 --> 00:40:34,150
We didn't know how to do things since we were born.

487
00:40:36,150 --> 00:40:38,150
Even if you start a little late,

488
00:40:39,150 --> 00:40:41,150
but I believe you can do it anyway.

489
00:40:42,150 --> 00:40:43,150
In the meantime,

490
00:40:44,150 --> 00:40:47,150
you just do a small job as I assign you.

491
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:52,150
I will teach you my yourself.

492
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,150
If you don't want to kill Tian,

493
00:41:09,150 --> 00:41:13,150
you have to find out what his secret is.

494
00:41:14,150 --> 00:41:15,150
If you are successful,

495
00:41:17,150 --> 00:41:19,150
it is considered that you save his life.

496
00:41:36,150 --> 00:41:38,150
Does Mr. Tian let you stay here?

497
00:41:42,150 --> 00:41:44,150
This room doesn't seem that far from my room.

498
00:41:45,150 --> 00:41:49,150
If you're lonely, you can go talk to me in my room.

499
00:42:00,150 --> 00:42:02,150
Mud, what's wrong?

500
00:42:04,150 --> 00:42:06,150
I don't know what bites my leg.

501
00:42:06,350 --> 00:42:07,150
Let me see it.

502
00:42:07,650 --> 00:42:10,150
Ouch, it hurts so much, right here.

503
00:42:11,150 --> 00:42:12,150
Can you see it?

504
00:42:29,150 --> 00:42:30,150
Jiu.

505
00:42:38,150 --> 00:42:39,150
How are you? Are you alright?

506
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:46,150
Tian.

507
00:42:48,150 --> 00:42:49,150
Jiu.

508
00:42:52,150 --> 00:42:53,150
What's wrong with the men in this house?

509
00:42:54,150 --> 00:42:56,150
Tian, Tian.

510
00:42:59,150 --> 00:43:00,150
You misunderstood now.

511
00:43:01,150 --> 00:43:02,150
What did I misunderstand?

512
00:43:04,150 --> 00:43:05,150
About me and Mud.

513
00:43:06,150 --> 00:43:07,150
What you do is up to you.

514
00:43:09,150 --> 00:43:11,150
Whether you like or fond of each other,

515
00:43:13,150 --> 00:43:14,150
it's none of my business anyway.

516
00:43:16,150 --> 00:43:17,150
Are you angry with me?

517
00:43:17,350 --> 00:43:18,150
Why would I be angry?

518
00:43:26,150 --> 00:43:27,150
Or do you...

519
00:43:31,150 --> 00:43:32,150
You like...

520
00:43:35,150 --> 00:43:36,150
You like Mud?

521
00:43:39,150 --> 00:43:40,150
Do you like her?

522
00:43:41,150 --> 00:43:42,150
No.

523
00:43:43,150 --> 00:43:44,150
You don't have to hide from me.

524
00:43:46,150 --> 00:43:47,150
I really don't like Mud.

525
00:43:50,150 --> 00:43:52,150
I never thought of her like that.

526
00:43:53,150 --> 00:43:55,150
I only see her as a member in the house.

527
00:43:57,150 --> 00:43:58,150
I don't like Mud either.

528
00:44:00,150 --> 00:44:02,150
It's impossible for me and her.

529
00:44:06,150 --> 00:44:08,150
Well, if you're not angry about me and Mud.

530
00:44:09,150 --> 00:44:10,150
Why are you angry with me?

531
00:44:12,150 --> 00:44:13,150
Forget it.

532
00:44:33,150 --> 00:44:35,150
Scales of beetle orchid.

533
00:44:39,150 --> 00:44:45,150
This tooth really came from the corpse of someone who was poisoned by the beetle orchid.

534
00:45:01,150 --> 00:45:02,150
Flowers, Madam.

535
00:45:05,150 --> 00:45:09,150
Aunt Jia said that you wanted flowers to pay homage to the Buddha.

536
00:45:10,150 --> 00:45:11,150
Thanks.

537
00:45:12,150 --> 00:45:15,150
I want to pay homage to the Buddha because I'm worried.

538
00:45:16,150 --> 00:45:17,150
I don't know what to do.

539
00:45:18,150 --> 00:45:20,150
What are you worried about, Madam?

540
00:45:22,150 --> 00:45:25,150
Someone wants me and Tian to split up.

541
00:45:28,150 --> 00:45:30,150
Telling my son about something crazy.

542
00:45:33,150 --> 00:45:36,150
Do you know who slandered me?

543
00:45:38,150 --> 00:45:39,150
No.

544
00:45:43,150 --> 00:45:44,150
Bua.

545
00:45:45,150 --> 00:45:49,150
Do you know that I love and trust you?

546
00:45:50,150 --> 00:45:53,150
To the point that I let you be another mother of Tian.

547
00:45:55,150 --> 00:45:59,150
In the past, the two of us have supported each other.

548
00:46:08,150 --> 00:46:10,150
We have helped each other all along.

549
00:46:12,150 --> 00:46:14,150
You won't leave me, right?

550
00:46:42,150 --> 00:46:44,150
No, Madam.

551
00:46:45,150 --> 00:46:48,150
If there's nothing, please excuse me.

552
00:46:50,150 --> 00:46:51,150
You can go now.

553
00:47:00,150 --> 00:47:01,150
Keep an eye on Bua.

554
00:47:03,150 --> 00:47:04,150
Yes, Madam.

555
00:47:09,150 --> 00:47:12,150
It seems like Madam Li started to suspect us.

556
00:47:12,650 --> 00:47:18,150
This morning, she said that someone had told Tian a slander on her.

557
00:47:20,150 --> 00:47:22,150
I'm the one who did it.

558
00:47:22,450 --> 00:47:23,150
Oh.

559
00:47:24,150 --> 00:47:27,150
I was the one who told Tian that I was suspicious of Madam and Aunt Jia.

560
00:47:28,150 --> 00:47:31,150
I told him about the blood sucking mushrooms and everything.

561
00:47:32,150 --> 00:47:35,150
From now on, Tian should be the one who decide for himself on what he wants.

562
00:47:37,150 --> 00:47:41,150
Then Madam Li said this to test me.

563
00:47:42,150 --> 00:47:46,150
We must be more careful, Yang.

564
00:48:04,150 --> 00:48:05,150
This one read 'Ngor Ngoo'.

565
00:48:07,150 --> 00:48:09,150
Ngor Ngoo. / Ngoo (snake).

566
00:48:11,150 --> 00:48:12,150
Ngoo.

567
00:48:12,450 --> 00:48:13,150
Ngoo.

568
00:48:13,450 --> 00:48:14,150
It's snake.

569
00:48:15,150 --> 00:48:16,150
Ngor Ngoo.

570
00:48:34,150 --> 00:48:35,150
This one reads Jor Jan.

571
00:48:36,150 --> 00:48:38,150
Your name is also written with this one.

572
00:48:39,150 --> 00:48:40,150
Jor Jan.

573
00:48:42,150 --> 00:48:44,150
So how do I write my name?

574
00:48:49,150 --> 00:48:50,150
I'll write it for you.

575
00:48:59,150 --> 00:49:00,150
Your name is written like this.

576
00:49:28,150 --> 00:49:29,150
I can write my name now.

577
00:49:31,150 --> 00:49:32,150
You're so quick-witted

578
00:49:33,150 --> 00:49:36,150
I taught you a little and you can do it fluently.

579
00:49:46,150 --> 00:49:48,150
I want my siblings to learn something like this.

580
00:49:52,150 --> 00:49:55,150
So they will have knowledge and not stupid like me.

581
00:49:58,150 --> 00:50:00,150
So their lives will have more options than me.

582
00:50:07,150 --> 00:50:08,150
It's alright.

583
00:50:10,150 --> 00:50:12,150
When Mei and Fu are feeling better,

584
00:50:13,150 --> 00:50:15,150
you can pick them up from your relative's house.

585
00:50:17,150 --> 00:50:19,150
I will find a way to enroll them in a school.

586
00:50:20,150 --> 00:50:22,150
Letting them live here with you.

587
00:50:24,150 --> 00:50:25,150
Thanks so much.

588
00:50:26,150 --> 00:50:27,150
You are really good to me.

589
00:51:07,150 --> 00:51:08,150
Well, how do you write your name?

590
00:51:42,150 --> 00:51:43,150
Tian.

591
00:51:45,150 --> 00:51:46,150
Father.

592
00:51:53,150 --> 00:51:54,150
Who is this?

593
00:51:59,150 --> 00:52:03,150
This is Jiu, the new worker I've hired.

594
00:52:06,150 --> 00:52:07,150
Sir.

595
00:52:37,150 --> 00:52:38,150
Your facial feature is good.

596
00:52:42,150 --> 00:52:43,150
Even if you have a hard time,

597
00:52:45,150 --> 00:52:47,150
there is always someone who helps you.

598
00:52:51,150 --> 00:52:54,150
Father, Jiu saved my life

599
00:52:54,350 --> 00:52:55,150
when I was attacked by Japanese soldiers.

600
00:52:58,150 --> 00:52:59,150
Really?

601
00:53:03,150 --> 00:53:05,150
You're a benefactor to Tian.

602
00:53:07,150 --> 00:53:08,150
Thank you very much

603
00:53:09,150 --> 00:53:10,150
for saving him.

604
00:53:12,150 --> 00:53:13,150
Yes, Sir.

605
00:53:16,150 --> 00:53:17,150
Good.

606
00:53:18,150 --> 00:53:19,150
You have someone you can trust close to you.

607
00:53:21,150 --> 00:53:22,150
So you can help each other.

608
00:53:24,150 --> 00:53:25,150
Yes, Father.

609
00:53:39,150 --> 00:53:40,150
Move.

610
00:53:40,450 --> 00:53:43,150
What's wrong?

611
00:53:43,150 --> 00:53:46,150
Jiu, eat more so that you will have energy to work.

612
00:53:48,150 --> 00:53:52,150
Oh, seeing a new male worker, you hurry to take care of him huh?

613
00:53:54,150 --> 00:54:01,150
You don't take care of Mr. Tian, giving him food anymore?

614
00:54:03,150 --> 00:54:08,150
Mr. Tian is our boss. I have to do my job.

615
00:54:09,150 --> 00:54:11,150
Are you really that close to Mr. Tian?

616
00:54:12,150 --> 00:54:14,150
Mud approaches all men.

617
00:54:15,150 --> 00:54:17,150
She's not close to anyone, she just wants men.

618
00:54:17,250 --> 00:54:18,150
Bitch.

619
00:54:18,350 --> 00:54:19,150
Be careful.

620
00:54:19,350 --> 00:54:20,150
Really.

621
00:54:22,150 --> 00:54:24,150
And who is Mr. Tian close to?

622
00:54:25,150 --> 00:54:28,150
As far as I can see, he is very close to Mr. Yang, his brother.

623
00:54:29,150 --> 00:54:31,150
Other than that, I don't see him messing with anyone. He always works.

624
00:54:33,150 --> 00:54:36,150
You're lucky to work here.

625
00:54:36,850 --> 00:54:41,150
Mr. Tian is kind, compassionate and humble.

626
00:54:42,150 --> 00:54:43,150
He never oppressed the workers.

627
00:54:43,450 --> 00:54:45,150
Everyone loves him. Do you think so?

628
00:54:46,150 --> 00:54:48,150
Yes. I'm really envious of Lady Pin.

629
00:54:49,150 --> 00:54:51,150
Lady Pin? Who is it?

630
00:54:52,150 --> 00:54:54,150
She's Mr. Tian's fiancée.

631
00:54:56,150 --> 00:54:57,150
Mr. Tian has a fiancée?

632
00:54:57,450 --> 00:54:58,150
Yeah.

633
00:55:08,150 --> 00:55:08,350
Here. Let your sister take the medicine.

634
00:55:08,350 --> 00:55:09,150
It's okay.
Here. Let your sister take the medicine.

635
00:55:09,150 --> 00:55:11,150
Here. Let your sister take the medicine.

636
00:55:11,350 --> 00:55:13,150
It's annoying that she cries.

637
00:55:15,150 --> 00:55:17,150
Mei, take the medicine.

638
00:55:31,150 --> 00:55:34,150
Aren't you feeling better now?

639
00:55:35,150 --> 00:55:36,150
It's alright.

640
00:55:38,150 --> 00:55:39,150
I'm hurt.

641
00:55:46,150 --> 00:55:48,150
Mei, you'll be alright.

642
00:55:51,150 --> 00:55:52,150
Hey, drink more.

643
00:56:09,150 --> 00:56:11,150
You'll be fine.

644
00:56:12,150 --> 00:56:13,150
You'll be better.

645
00:56:14,150 --> 00:56:16,150
I miss Jiu.

646
00:56:16,350 --> 00:56:17,150
I miss him too.

647
00:56:19,150 --> 00:56:21,150
Let him do his job first.

648
00:56:21,350 --> 00:56:24,150
When he finishes, he will pick us up. Hang in there.

649
00:56:28,150 --> 00:56:29,150
You two must take care of each other.

650
00:56:30,150 --> 00:56:32,150
Don't cry too loud. It's annoying.

651
00:56:34,150 --> 00:56:37,150
Hey, talk nicely to the kids.

652
00:56:48,150 --> 00:56:50,150
Don't worry, boy.

653
00:56:51,150 --> 00:56:52,150
I will take care of you.

654
00:56:58,150 --> 00:57:02,150
Sir, that girl is addicted to opium and is now in serious condition.

655
00:57:03,150 --> 00:57:06,150
Increase the quantity and take good care of her.

656
00:57:08,150 --> 00:57:11,150
Increase too much will kill her.

657
00:57:12,150 --> 00:57:13,150
Be careful.

658
00:57:14,150 --> 00:57:16,150
If those two kids are still with us,

659
00:57:17,150 --> 00:57:20,150
Jiu will do anything for us.

660
00:57:21,150 --> 00:57:22,150
Yes, Sir.

661
00:57:29,150 --> 00:57:30,150
Come in.

662
00:57:45,150 --> 00:57:46,150
Come in.

663
00:57:50,150 --> 00:57:51,150
What's wrong?

664
00:57:51,750 --> 00:57:54,150
Mr. Song would like to meet you and Jia.

665
00:58:12,150 --> 00:58:13,150
Doctor Qi.

666
00:58:18,150 --> 00:58:20,150
What's wrong?

667
00:58:34,150 --> 00:58:35,150
Li, Jia.

668
00:58:37,150 --> 00:58:39,150
Let me get this straight.

669
00:58:40,150 --> 00:58:44,150
I know about the blood sucking mushrooms and the beetle orchids already.

670
00:58:48,150 --> 00:58:50,150
What are you talking about? I don't get it.

671
00:58:53,150 --> 00:58:56,150
The day before, I dug where the blood sucking mushrooms grew.

672
00:58:58,150 --> 00:59:00,150
I found this tooth.

673
00:59:17,150 --> 00:59:19,150
I had it checked by Doctor Qi.

674
00:59:20,150 --> 00:59:22,150
So I know that the owner of this tooth

675
00:59:24,150 --> 00:59:25,150
died because of the beetle orchids.

676
00:59:26,150 --> 00:59:28,150
You two used the beetle orchids to kill someone

677
00:59:29,150 --> 00:59:31,150
to hide Tian's secret, right?

678
00:59:38,150 --> 00:59:39,150
No.

679
00:59:40,150 --> 00:59:41,150
There's no secret at all.

680
00:59:41,350 --> 00:59:42,150
Stop lying.

681
00:59:47,150 --> 00:59:49,150
If you still have the dignity of the Song family's first madam…

682
00:59:52,150 --> 00:59:53,150
Li.

683
00:59:55,150 --> 00:59:56,150
What is Tian's secret?

684
00:59:58,150 --> 01:00:00,150
Why would you kill someone to cover up?

685
01:00:02,150 --> 01:00:05,150
It's because I'm the first madam, so I said this.

686
01:00:07,150 --> 01:00:10,150
I didn't do anything wrong. Don't accuse me.

687
01:00:11,150 --> 01:00:13,150
The evidence is in front of you.

688
01:00:14,150 --> 01:00:15,150
You still don't accept it?

689
01:00:15,350 --> 01:00:17,150
What's the evidence?

690
01:00:17,950 --> 01:00:21,150
You found a tooth from someone's dead body and then accused me.

691
01:00:25,150 --> 01:00:31,150
How can a teacher not recognize his students' work?

692
01:00:33,150 --> 01:00:37,150
The owner of this tooth died from being poisoned by the beetle orchid.

693
01:00:39,150 --> 01:00:40,150
Doctor.

694
01:00:42,150 --> 01:00:45,150
You might teach this knowledge to others.

695
01:00:46,150 --> 01:00:50,150
Now, that person would probably frame me because he knew that I know about it.

696
01:00:51,150 --> 01:00:55,150
I taught you to use it to help people, not to hurt someone like this.

697
01:00:55,350 --> 01:00:56,150
And you are still not speaking the truth?

698
01:01:03,150 --> 01:01:04,150
Bao.

699
01:01:04,350 --> 01:01:05,150
Yes, Sir.

700
01:01:06,150 --> 01:01:07,150
Go to Jia's room.

701
01:01:09,150 --> 01:01:11,150
Search for the beetle orchid.

702
01:01:11,350 --> 01:01:12,150
Yes, Sir.

703
01:01:32,150 --> 01:01:35,150
That servant. I let her find mushrooms. Where has she been now?

704
01:01:36,150 --> 01:01:37,150
Will she get something?

705
01:01:43,150 --> 01:01:44,150
Doctor Qi.

706
01:01:46,150 --> 01:01:47,150
How did he come here?

707
01:01:50,150 --> 01:01:51,150
Something happens?

708
01:01:54,150 --> 01:01:55,150
Madam.

709
01:01:56,150 --> 01:01:57,150
Nuan, I'm shocked.

710
01:01:58,150 --> 01:01:59,150
I saw … I saw…

711
01:01:59,350 --> 01:02:03,150
It doesn't matter bow. Something happens here. Let's go. Quickly.

712
01:02:03,350 --> 01:02:04,150
Well...

713
01:02:05,150 --> 01:02:06,150
Madam. Alright.

714
01:02:20,150 --> 01:02:21,150
Bao.

715
01:02:21,650 --> 01:02:22,150
Yes, Sir.

716
01:02:35,150 --> 01:02:37,150
Madam, Madam.

717
01:03:19,150 --> 01:03:20,150
There's nothing, Sir.

718
01:03:44,150 --> 01:03:46,150
I can't find the beetle orchid, Sir.

719
01:03:48,150 --> 01:03:50,150
I didn't find anything.

720
01:04:07,150 --> 01:04:10,150
I told you that Jia and I didn't do it.

721
01:04:14,150 --> 01:04:17,150
Or did you do it but cover it up completely?

722
01:04:18,150 --> 01:04:22,150
If you think I did it, find the evidence.

723
01:04:24,150 --> 01:04:26,150
Where did she hide the evidence?

724
01:04:27,150 --> 01:04:28,150
I know.

725
01:04:29,150 --> 01:04:30,150
What?

726
01:04:30,650 --> 01:04:32,150
I'm going to tell you now.

727
01:04:32,650 --> 01:04:35,150
You can't accuse me without any evidence like this.

728
01:04:35,650 --> 01:04:37,150
No witnesses, no evidence.

729
01:04:38,150 --> 01:04:40,150
I have one.

730
01:04:50,150 --> 01:04:51,150
Chan.

731
01:04:52,150 --> 01:04:54,150
Are you eavesdropping?

732
01:04:54,650 --> 01:04:56,150
Please talk about manners later, Sir.

733
01:04:56,450 --> 01:04:58,150
Now there's something bigger than that.

734
01:04:58,350 --> 01:05:01,150
Nuan, tell me what you saw.

735
01:05:02,150 --> 01:05:06,150
I saw Aunt Jia buried those orchids in the forest at the back of the house.

736
01:05:09,150 --> 01:05:14,150
Madam wants to find out how Madam Li and Jia killed,

737
01:05:15,150 --> 01:05:17,150
but she let me find the mushrooms alone.

738
01:06:07,150 --> 01:06:08,150
You really want to die.

739
01:06:12,150 --> 01:06:14,150
Don't talk nonsense.

740
01:06:15,150 --> 01:06:17,150
Do you want to join Mr. Song to slander me?

741
01:06:18,150 --> 01:06:20,150
Don't argue.

742
01:06:20,350 --> 01:06:22,150
Nuan, take me there now.

743
01:06:22,650 --> 01:06:23,150
Yes, Sir.

744
01:06:54,150 --> 01:06:55,150
This way, please.

745
01:07:05,150 --> 01:07:06,150
Bao.

746
01:07:06,450 --> 01:07:07,150
Yes, Sir.

747
01:07:10,150 --> 01:07:11,150
Where is it?

748
01:07:11,650 --> 01:07:12,150
Here.

749
01:07:32,150 --> 01:07:34,150
Wow, there are so many people. Will I have a chance to try?

750
01:07:34,450 --> 01:07:35,150
You will, Mr. Yang.

751
01:07:36,150 --> 01:07:38,150
Everyone, stop. Stop!

752
01:07:38,550 --> 01:07:40,150
Go to the forest at the back of our house now.

753
01:07:41,150 --> 01:07:44,150
The fact that Dong was killed is about to be revealed.

754
01:07:46,150 --> 01:07:48,150
Madam Li did it all.

755
01:07:51,150 --> 01:07:53,150
Mom, what are you doing?

756
01:07:53,450 --> 01:07:55,150
Yang, I didn't do anything.

757
01:07:56,150 --> 01:07:58,150
It's your madam.

758
01:08:01,150 --> 01:08:04,150
She killed Dong to hide a secret for Tian.

759
01:08:04,450 --> 01:08:08,150
Today is the day that I will get the evidence to arrest her.

760
01:08:22,150 --> 01:08:23,150
Let's work hard, Bao.

761
01:08:25,150 --> 01:08:26,150
I can remember. It's here.

762
01:08:55,150 --> 01:08:56,150
Sir.

763
01:09:02,150 --> 01:09:03,150
Chan.

764
01:09:04,150 --> 01:09:06,150
Why did you call everyone?

765
01:09:08,150 --> 01:09:12,150
I didn't. I just walked by and everyone follow me.

766
01:09:13,150 --> 01:09:14,150
But that's good.

767
01:09:14,450 --> 01:09:17,150
Everyone here will be able to see the evidence at the same time.

768
01:09:18,150 --> 01:09:21,150
What did Madam and Jia use to kill Dong?

769
01:09:22,150 --> 01:09:23,150
Chan.

770
01:09:28,150 --> 01:09:32,150
Dong is dead because of Jia's bizarre insects.

771
01:09:33,150 --> 01:09:36,150
The corpse would be so strange that it couldn't be seen by others.

772
01:09:36,650 --> 01:09:39,150
Therefore, they had to steal the body and buried it at the back of the house.

773
01:09:48,150 --> 01:09:51,150
And the mushrooms that all of you had

774
01:09:52,150 --> 01:09:53,150
grew from Dong's corpse.

775
01:09:54,150 --> 01:09:56,150
Huh? Mushrooms from Dong's corpse?

776
01:09:58,150 --> 01:09:59,150
Right.

777
01:10:00,150 --> 01:10:04,150
The mushrooms are from the orchid that we are about to see it together.

778
01:10:22,150 --> 01:10:23,150
We’ve found the box, Sir.

779
01:10:50,150 --> 01:10:54,150
This box is the one Jia buried.

780
01:11:52,150 --> 01:11:53,150
We’ve found the box, Sir.

781
01:11:58,150 --> 01:11:59,150
This is…

782
01:11:59,650 --> 01:12:02,150
Who are they? Your kids?

783
01:12:03,150 --> 01:12:04,150
Tian.
